    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED\nAIR LINES\nA WORLD'S\nSTANDARD FOR\nSPEED PLUS LUXURY\n14½ hours from California to New York with\nonly 3 stops ... Chicago to New York non-stop\nin 3 hours 55 minutes ... Los Angeles-San\nFrancisco 2 hours. These United Mainliners,\nbuilt by Douglas, are the largest, most power-\nful, most luxurious transports in the U.S. Backed\nby 110,000,000 miles of flying experience.\nPOST CARD\nPlease address\nand return to\nstewardess who\nwill stamp and\nmail card\nfor you."
